docs.lead_paragraph: ORCHAHD STREET, on the lower east side. Never heard of it? It is one block east of Allen Street, famed throughout the country for its copper and brass ware. Admire a piece of brassware uptown, and you can buy its duplicate in Allen Street at half the price.
docs.abstract: Feature article, When Orchard Street Buys
